CookDC® entered one of its meal kits in a competition with 500 attendees and won based on their vote....this is the same meal our customers cooked themselves two days prior  By providing restaurant quality ingredients, recipes based on classical technique, and clear instructions, CookDC® is "Turning Home Cooks into Chefs."®
